CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "Feast of the Frogs - New World A' Comin'!  P. L. Prattis, executive editor of The Pittsburgh Courier, addresses the Frog Symposium at Loendi Club Sunday, giving his interpretation of the San Francisco Conference which he covered.  A portion of the audience which heard him can be seen in the right-hand picture.  The Symposium at Loendi started the annual Frog Week program off.  A picnic and private affairs featured celebration. - All Photos By Harris."
TitMainTitle: P. L. Prattis addressing small crowd at symposium in Loendi Club for FROGS week event
